https://openjfx.io/openjfx-docs/#introduction

Set up SDK 11 with JavaFX, which is not included in Java SDK anymore

Appearance and Behaviour -> Path Variables -> Create new to lib in JavaFX folder (download from github)

Set variable PATH_TO_FX

runtime Enviroment Configuration :

--module-path ${PATH_TO_FX} --add-modules=javafx.controls,javafx.fxml